{"tid":853621,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美軍傳台海軍演 台港股驚剉","createTime":"2018-10-08T17:17:33.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-09T03:17:40.000Z","uid":35790,"like":14,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"2667f2e50980b9ee5536d1e68f2b65a9ea590a93","tid":853621,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T17:17:33.000Z","msg":"美軍傳台海軍演 台港股驚剉<br />\n<br />\n2018-10-04 14:35 聯合晚報 記者李娟萍、葉子菁／台北報導<br />\n<br />\n台股6度跌破年線<br />\n外傳美軍擬在台灣海峽、南海軍演一周「警示大陸」，今嚇傻台、港股市。台股今（4）日盤中大跌近140點，跌破10,829的年線支撐，並寫下今年第六度跌破年線；港股恒指更大跌470點，直接摜破27,000點，香港國企股也大跌逾200點，跌幅逾2%，居今日亞股跌幅最大的重災區。<br />\n<br />\n台北股市今天開低走低，收盤大跌145.03點，為10718.91點，跌幅1.33%，成交金額新台幣1097.60億元。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.google.com/amp/s/udn.com/news/amp/story/7250/3403063\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Famp%2Fs%2Fudn.com%2Fnews%2Famp%2Fstory%2F7250%2F3403063&d=hX7LktZw2xj3frkISH%2FJasPrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=7b1253fa\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com/amp/s/udn.com/news/amp/story/7250/3403063</a><br />\n<br />\n主要係因中美貿易戰<br />\n及美副總統發表中國政策演說"},{"pid":"cfccf643c36503bd3ef8d4e0343e16c1e76626c3","tid":853621,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T17:22:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89b6c089db35040b122e3efd45be1467875c3079","tid":853621,"uid":35790,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T17:41:56.000Z","msg":"呢幾日 中國股市一樣係大跌<br />\n上證最多跌3.7%<br />\n唔通又跟美軍台海軍演有關"},{"pid":"da04c02483abe0485afdcf4201cb05d7caaca9c5","tid":853621,"uid":147314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T17:46:07.000Z","msg":"<strong>期指夜市收報25997 低水206點</strong><br />\n <br />\n夜市期指收報25997點，跌152點，較昨日恒指收市26202點，低水206點，成交42142張。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/hongkong/article/1961870/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Finstantnews%2Fhongkong%2Farticle%2F1961870%2F&